China's Family Planning Army

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Lucy Ash, published by BBC broadcasted as part of BBC Our World series in 2016 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/9/91/China-s-Family-Planning-Army-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Lucy Ash visits a pilot project in Shaanxi Province. Former enforcers there are being trained up to offer advice and support to rural grandparents who are left rearing children while parents migrate to jobs in the big cities.
